query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS suppliers (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  companyName VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  contactPerson VARCHAR(255),
  email VARCHAR(255),
  phone VARCHAR(50),
  address TEXT,
  country VARCHAR(100),
  status VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'active',
  createdAt BIGINT NOT NULL,
  updatedAt BIGINT
);
